Revision history for Class-Accessor-Classy

v0.9.1 2009-07-13

  * better lw() documentation

  * 'About' documentation

v0.9.0 2008-02-18

  * lv() lvalue accessor/mutator maker

  * documentation for the frontend 'maker' functions

v0.1.3 2007-04-22

  * ri() immutable accessor maker

  * play nice with Module::Refresh

  * getter/setter overrides for *some* types

v0.1.2 2007-02-26

  * dereferenced-list accessors

  * class accessors

  * reporting

  * introspection (experimental)

v0.1.1 2006-11-01

  * initial release

